      <h4>Best Plant Synthetic Biology</h4>
      <p>This award is designed to celebrate exemplary work done in plant synthetic biology. Did you build a project in a plant chassis? Did you submit plant parts to the Registry? This award could also be given to a team working with algae or another eukaryotic photosynthetic chassis. Show us what you made and remember to adhere to iGEM safety guidelines!</p>
      <p><i>Note: Photosynthetic bacteria cannot be considered for this prize.</i></p>
      <hr />
      <p>Visit the <a href="https://competition.igem.org/judging/special-prizes">Special Prizes page</a> for more information.</p>
